law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491, effective January 2, 1978. -- Amended 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 73, sec. 1, effective May 18, 1956. -- Created 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 7, sec. 5.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Ineligibility because of previous service or because name not on property valuation administrator's book or voter's registration book.
